1. 学习June_23未学完的知识点



1. to_sql结合from使用
    如:
        score_records = ScoreRecord.all
        rails_sql = score_records.group("competition_scores.competition_team_id ,competition_scores.user_id").select("SUM(cost_time) times, SUM(score) all_score, competition_scores.user_id user_id, competition_team_id").to_sql
        puts rails_sql => 打印mysql查询语句

    想针对rails_sql中零时表操作时候要结合from的使用
    如:
        score_records.select("SUM(a.xxx)").from("(#{rails_sql}) as test_table").group("test_table.xxx, score_records.xxx ").order("xx")
        一般建from前直接使用rails_sql的原model
        如: ScoreRecords.from........


